citations:
    citation-agot-catelyn-i:
        source: source-agot
        properties:
            locator: "Catelyn I"
            accessed: "2026-03-06"
        notes: "POV: Catelyn. Catelyn finds Ned cleaning Ice in the godswood after the execution. Ned discusses the Night's Watch's troubles and Mance Rayder. Maester Luwin delivers news that Jon Arryn is dead and King Robert is riding north. A secret letter from Lysa Arryn arrives in a carved box with a false-bottom, alleging the Lannisters murdered Jon Arryn."
